5:["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L1d",null,{"value":[{"value":"What you’ll find here","id":"what-youll-find-here","depth":2},{"value":"Source","id":"source","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L1e",null,{}],["$","$L1f",null,{"metadata":{"title":"Introduction","filePath":"content/index.mdx"},"bottomContent":"$undefined","sourceCode":"---\ntitle: Introduction\n---\n\n# Flashycardy Docs\n\nWelcome to the documentation site for **Flashycardy**, a full-stack flashcard app built on Next.js 16, Drizzle, Clerk, and the Vercel AI SDK.\n\nThis site is intentionally minimal for now — it ships as a placeholder to validate the monorepo + Vercel deployment of `apps/docs`. Content will be backfilled in follow-up work.\n\n## What you'll find here\n\n- **Getting Started** — clone, install, and run locally.\n- **Architecture** — how the monorepo and the web app are organized.\n\n## Source\n\nThe Flashycardy app and these docs live in the same monorepo. The web app is at `apps/web`; this docs site is at `apps/docs`.","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"id":"$undefined","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["Flashycardy Docs","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["Welcome to the documentation site for ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Flashycardy"}],", a full-stack flashcard app built on Next.js 16, Drizzle, Clerk, and the Vercel AI SDK."]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["This site is intentionally minimal for now — it ships as a placeholder to validate the monorepo + Vercel deployment of ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"apps/docs"}],". Content will be backfilled in follow-up work."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"wha